  "text": "International Civil Aviation Organization (ICAO) has constrained control and communication data links to [CITATION_1] . The ICAO tries to make sure that the allocated spectrum for UAS data links and command and control are either in AM(R)S or AMS(R)S, while they do not impact the performance of other aerial systems.",
